<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error <%= status %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ff5c5c;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        a {
            color: #ff5c5c;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= status %></h1>
        <h2><%= message %></h2>
        <p>Maaf, terjadi kesalahan. Silakan kembali ke halaman utama.</p>
        <a href="/">Beranda</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
